title: Oct 09, 2015 September NCUA Board Video Now Available (NCUA - National Credit Union Administration) ...
text: ( Source : NCUA - National Credit Union Administration ) ALEXANDRIA, Va. (Oct. 9, 2015 ) - The video recording of the September 2015 open meeting of the National Credit Union Administration Board is now available on the agency's website.
